snippet.title: Best VGM 1211 - Zelda : Skyward Sword - Koloktos Battle (Phase 2)
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii
Zelda : Skyward Sword (2011)
Koloktos Battle (Phase 2)
Hajime Wakai, Koji Kondo, Mahito Yokota, Shiho Fujii & Takeshi Hama

Image source : http://jesseuhhyeah.deviantart.com/art/Ancient-Automaton-Koloktos-310532316
